---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Juvederm Fillers | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Hyaluronic acid dermal fillers to restore volume, soften folds, enhance lips, and refine contours—natural, reversible, and tailored dosing.',
  canonical: '/services/juvederm-fillers/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Juvederm Fillers',
      serviceType: 'Hyaluronic Acid Dermal Fillers',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      },
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/juvederm-fillers/'
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Injectables</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Juvederm Fillers</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        Hyaluronic acid fillers that integrate smoothly for refined volume, softer folds, and balanced, natural contours.
        Dosed conservatively and designed to age well.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Longevity</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~9–24 months</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Contains</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Hyaluronic acid</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Minimal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Reversible</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Yes (hyaluronidase)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">
      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Juvederm is a family of hyaluronic acid (HA) dermal fillers designed to restore lost volume, soften
            moderate-to-deep folds, enhance lips, and refine facial contours. Modern crosslinking technologies help the
            gel last longer in tissue while maintaining a smooth, natural look and feel.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We select specific formulations and techniques based on facial anatomy, skin quality, and goals, prioritizing
            balance and restraint so you look refreshed—never overfilled.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Common treatment areas</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Cheeks & midface',
                'Nasolabial folds',
                'Marionette lines',
                'Lips & lip border',
                'Chin projection',
                'Jawline definition'
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Final product choice and technique are individualized after assessment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            During consultation we review medical history, assess dynamic and static lines, and map volume needs.
            On treatment day, the skin is cleansed, a topical anesthetic may be used, and product is placed with
            microcannula and/or fine needle. Gentle molding helps the gel integrate smoothly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">The session</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Photos and plan review</li>
                <li>Numbing as needed (many HA fillers contain lidocaine)</li>
                <li>Precise placement by layer and vector</li>
                <li>Typical time: ~15–60 minutes depending on areas</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Results timeline</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Immediate volume change</li>
                <li>Days 1–7: swelling/bruising settle</li>
                <li>1–2 weeks: result “sets” and refines</li>
                <li>Longevity varies by area and product (~9–24 months)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">A conservative philosophy</div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
                We start modestly and can layer over time. HA fillers are reversible with hyaluronidase if clinically
                indicated, adding a margin of safety and flexibility.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid rubbing, pressing, or massaging treated areas for 24 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Use cool compresses in short intervals if swelling occurs.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Limit heavy makeup on day one; keep skin clean and protected.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid strenuous exercise, heat, and sauna for 24–48 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Daily SPF; limit direct sun while swelling resolves.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Follow your clinician’s guidance regarding meds and supplements.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety & risks -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & risks</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, temporary effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Swelling, redness, tenderness</li>
              <li>Small bruises at entry points</li>
              <li>Temporary firmness or mild asymmetry as product settles</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Less common risks</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Nodules, migration, infection</li>
              <li>Irregularities or persistent asymmetry</li>
              <li>
                Vascular occlusion (urgent): sudden blanching, severe pain, or vision changes—seek immediate care.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Educational information only; not medical advice. Candidacy, product selection, and technique are determined by your clinician.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How long do results last?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Longevity depends on the product, area, and metabolism. Many results last between 9 and 24 months.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Will it look “overdone”?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Our approach is conservative and anatomy-led. We prioritize balance and proportion so results look like you—rested, not “filled.”
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Does it hurt?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Most patients find it very tolerable. Many HA fillers include lidocaine, and we can add topical numbing when appropriate.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Can it be reversed?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Yes—HA fillers can be dissolved with hyaluronidase if clinically needed.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Ready to explore a filler plan tailored to your features and goals?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
